items.question: ある
items.answer: to be,to have (used for inanimate objects)

items.question: 居る
items.answer: to be, to have (used for people and animals)

items.question: 聞く
items.answer: to hear, to listen to, to ask

items.question: 着る
items.answer: to put on from the shoulders down

items.question: 曇る
items.answer: to become cloudy, to become dim

items.question: 消す
items.answer: to erase, to turn off power

items.question: 差す
items.answer: to stretch out hands, to raise an umbrella

items.question: 撮る
items.answer: to take a photo or record a film

items.question: 鳴く
items.answer: animal noise. to chirp, roar or croak etc.

items.question: 並ぶ
items.answer: to line up,to stand in a line

items.question: 弾く
items.answer: to play an instrument with strings, including piano

items.question: 二日
items.answer: two days, second day of the month

items.question: 降る
items.answer: to fall, e.g. rain or snow

items.question: 三日
items.answer: three days, third day of the month

items.question: 六日
items.answer: six days, sixth day of the month

items.question: 八日
items.answer: eight days, eighth day of the month

items.question: 四日
items.answer: four days, fouth day of the month

items.question: ラジカセ / ラジオカセット
